                     <interp inst="t18410201-649-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18410201-cd-69" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410201-649-offence-1 t18410201-cd-69"></join>12th of January</rs>, I watch, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410201-name-437" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-437" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-437" type="surname" value="BARNES"></interp>
